extract: Here are some of the most commonly used functions, and their graphs:Linear Function: f(x) = mx + b.Square Function: f(x) = x2Cube Function: f(x) = x3Square Root Function: f(x) = √x.Absolute Value Function: f(x) = |x|Reciprocal Function. f(x) = 1/x.
extract_html:
Here are some of the most commonly used functions, and their graphs:
  • Linear Function: f(x) = mx + b.
  • Square Function: f(x) = x2
  • Cube Function: f(x) = x3
  • Square Root Function: f(x) = √x.
  • Absolute Value Function: f(x) = |x|
  • Reciprocal Function. f(x) = 1/x.
